<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>メンテナンス中 | <%= site_name %></title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="<%= asset_path('favicon.svg') %>">
</head>
<body class="font-sans antialiased">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 via-white to-orange-50 flex items-center justify-center py-8 px-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl mb-4 shadow-lg">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-2">メンテナンス中</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-md mx-auto"><%= site_name %></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Card -->
      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-white/20 p-6 md:p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="text-center space-y-6">
          <!-- Maintenance Icon -->
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-100 to-orange-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Maintenance Message -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">システムメンテナンス中</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
              現在、システムのメンテナンスを実施しております。<br>
              ご不便をおかけして大変申し訳ございません。
            </p>
            
            <!-- Maintenance Details -->
            <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl p-4 max-w-sm mx-auto">
              <p class="text-sm text-amber-800 font-medium">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 inline mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                メンテナンス完了後、自動的にご利用いただけます
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Status Information -->
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
              <span>メンテナンス実施中</span>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 max-w-sm mx-auto">
              管理者の方は、管理者権限でアクセスできます。<br>
              緊急時は管理者にお問い合わせください。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Information (if needed) -->
          <div class="pt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
              ご質問がある場合は、管理者までお問い合わせください
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer Info -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          サービス一時停止中: <%= Time.current.strftime("%Y年%m月%d日 %H:%M") %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>